<lyrics>[V1]
 1. Thagau satang leh gitloh gik puo a,
 Lungkham liengvai taka ka um lai in;
 Kalvari thing hansedawl kraws ah chun,
 Ka Lalpa'n zawhna ei pie tai.

[V2]
 Aw Kraws, Aw kraws,
 Aw Kraws, kei gilo thiemchan na;
 Aw Kraws, Aw Kraws,
 Aw Kraws kei ei chawi sang tu.

[V3]
 2. Kei migilo buok thilhih theih neilo,
 Phat kana guot zing theihna ma suonin;
 Lungkham taka thavai himah lengle,
 Ka Lalpa'n zawhna ei pie tai.

[V4]
 3. Kei migilo mangsa kikhenden in,
 Keimah a hin Lal Krista a hing tai;
 Khawvel in ei subuoi thei ta puona,
 Ka Lalpa'n zawh na ei pie tai.

[V5]
 4. Damsung in lungkham buoina tung mahleh,
 Lau puongka Lal Krista ka phaw ahi;
 Nicheng Amah pahchak nan la sang ka,
 Ka Lalpan ei zawh sak ziekin.</lyrics>
<title>Aw Kraws</title>
</song>